// Phase 159q (audit #6) — explicit payment settlement state. Physical-POS sales
// record COMPLETED (the cashier confirms payment in person); the PENDING/FAILED
// states are for a future integrated payment-gateway flow flipped via webhook.
enum PosPaymentStatus {
